One of the largest [[City/Legends|cities]] on [[Commenor/Legends|Commenor]], '''Chasin City''' was famous for its restaurants.

Visitors to the city were offered a wide variety of incredible cooking styles and dining atmospheres.

Chasin City also featured a [[Plenty's]].

